ing hate back, I (Archer) ended up tanking until the Voke timer was up.  <br /> <br />Aurelius was talking about this in another thread. Phalanx to build hate, Voke/Taunt as a panic button if the mob jets on you. Seems like stacking low Stam/TP cost moves with short cooldowns beats using a high Stam and long cooldown move to set the hate line.  <br /> <br />Thoughts? <br /> <br />-Kash<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>I &quot;BAM!&quot; therefor I AM!</div></div>
