      <div class="msgContentFrame">There is an other reason why Cure can be a problem for keeping hate, the MP issus... In FFXI you could just have a Refresh in HL or just sit for 2-3 min and have some MP back. In FFXIV its a little harder to have some, there is still some ability to help gaining mp but if you need to use these ability in the fight for have MP it mean you lose this time to use a real Gladiator ability for gaining Enmity that wont cost you MP and can help you gain SP at the same time. Cure is still good to have for a lifesaver when your in trouble, like Second Wind, but i wont use it for help with Enmity. For now at my lvl (20) Provoke+Taunt and Phalanx are really enough for keeping hate.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/965232.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
